root: ^Yeah it’s been rough, thanks for asking.
^God you always know just what to say.
^I need to know who the father is.
^I cannot have a child out of wedlock, it would kill my mother.
^Barely hanging on, but she’s a fighter.
^Her husband cheated on her with her uncle.
^Oh girl don’t even get me started on him, lost all his money buying some internet coin.
^He wanted me to invest, can you believe it?? I had to ghost him.
^If you ask me, it’s all just a scam.
^I have a lot going on, okay?!
^Being pregnant isn’t all there is to me.
^I don’t even know how to figure out who’s the father.
^I won’t be shamed for having an active sex life.
^It prevents you from going blind early.
